<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Last nite someone gave me a tell and ask me how much this hammer worths and I gave an estimation of 4-7k, I really don't see much use of this hammer. First of all you will never use it when you grouping, shaman needs wis and AC when in a group and the combination of paw and CGS gives 18 more AC and 9 more wis. Also, even when soloing, I doubt that melee is the most efficient way as you have to keep all the buffs on yourself and alaricty or even celerity which will take too much mana IMO, and our pet summoned from our 55 pet spell just kick too much asses and we now also have an alternative way to do damages without using mana- JB bracer, so 4-7k is how much I will value this thing, just my 2cents.</font></td></tr></table>
