<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Blight Hammer of Scourge does proc for me and I'm level 35.  I kept up 1hb and 2hb so I do okay with it.  I have not used it much yet but I have hit for damage in the 50's and 60's.  I was just getting into using spears but perhaps I'll stick with the blunt weapons.  Yes you do lose some wisdom and AC with the hammer, but with the hammer I'm still at 189 wis and approx 640 AC (with shaman buffs).  I actually bought this weapon along with a Flayed Tourmoilskin Belt (Shaman only AC9 Wis5 Dex5) for a combined total of 8kpp.  But I think the guy was 50ish level and had money to spare so he wasn't to concerned about the amount, which was okay by me.  :)<BR>
